author: Craig CustanceESPN Senior Writer
description: Pittsburgh's Phil Kessel wears his emotions on his jersey and often wears out whoever's next to him on the bench or the ice. But the chatty winger's motives are more selfless than they may seem.
title: Kessel's passion play fires up Pens

author: Craig CustanceESPN Senior Writer
description: Frustrated and animated on the bench, playoff stud Phil Kessel lit a fire under the Penguins and pushed them to a Game 2 victory over the Senators, equaling the conference finals 1-1.
title: Angry Kessel gets it done for Penguins
